	title = {The {Ability} of the {Aryl} {Hydrocarbon} {Receptor} to {Regulate} {Ovarian} {Follicle} {Growth} and {Estradiol} {Biosynthesis} in {Mice} {Depends} on {Stage} of {Sexual} {Maturity}},
